-- Fortress Says Chief Executive Officer Daniel Mudd Resigned
-- B y   J e r a n   W i t t e n s t e i n
-- 2012-01-24T23:42:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/fortress-says-ceo-daniel-mudd-resigned.html
Fortress Investment Group said
 Daniel Mudd , who was sued by the U.S. Securities and Exchange
Commission over his previous role at  Fannie Mae , resigned today
as chief executive officer.  Mudd, who had been on a leave of absence from Fortress, was
formerly CEO of Fannie Mae.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeran Wittenstein at 
 jwittenstei1@bloomberg.net  